pg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/powder-room-080725-1017-11-800x961.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/powder-room-080725-1017-11-768x923.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/powder-room-080725-1017-11-1278x1536.jpg 1278w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/powder-room-080725-1017-11-1704x2048.jpg 1704w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eJust beyond a preserved archway, the loft opens into a light-filled gallery and conservatory where the owners’ piano takes center stage. Framed by clean lines and soft natural light, this area becomes a quiet zone for creativity and reflection. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1281\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/music-room-080725-1017-12.jpg\" alt=\"Framed by natural light, the loft\u0026#39;s conservatory features a piano at its heart. A calm, creative space for music, art, and reflection in the home.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/music-room-080725-1017-12.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/music-room-080725-1017-12-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/music-room-080725-1017-12-800x534.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/music-room-080725-1017-12-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/music-room-080725-1017-12-1536x1025.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/music-room-080725-1017-13.jpg\" alt=\"Framed by natural light, the loft\u0026#39;s conservatory features a piano at its heart. A calm, creative space for music, art, and reflection in the home.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/music-room-080725-1017-13.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/music-room-080725-1017-13-940x1253.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/music-room-080725-1017-13-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/music-room-080725-1017-13-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/music-room-080725-1017-13-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/music-room-080725-1017-13-1536x2048.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eElmire’s built-in shelving doubles as both storage and structure. Integrated into the oak frameworks, these shelves help define spatial boundaries and provide a continuous sense of flow, tying the spaces together visually.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/built-in-bookshelf-080725-1016-14.jpg\" alt=\"Built-in shelves blend seamlessly into architectural oak volumes, offering storage and structure while keeping the visual flow calm and cohesive.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/built-in-bookshelf-080725-1016-14.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/built-in-bookshelf-080725-1016-14-940x1253.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/built-in-bookshelf-080725-1016-14-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/built-in-bookshelf-080725-1016-14-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/built-in-bookshelf-080725-1016-14-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/built-in-bookshelf-080725-1016-14-1536x2048.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1281\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/built-in-bookshelf-080725-1016-15.jpg\" alt=\"Built-in shelves blend seamlessly into architectural oak volumes, offering storage and structure while keeping the visual flow calm and cohesive.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/built-in-bookshelf-080725-1016-15.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/built-in-bookshelf-080725-1016-15-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/built-in-bookshelf-080725-1016-15-800x534.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/built-in-bookshelf-080725-1016-15-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/built-in-bookshelf-080725-1016-15-1536x1025.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/built-in-bookshelf-080725-1016-16.jpg\" alt=\"Built-in shelves blend seamlessly into architectural oak volumes, offering storage and structure while keeping the visual flow calm and cohesive.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/built-in-bookshelf-080725-1016-16.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/built-in-bookshelf-080725-1016-16-940x1253.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/built-in-bookshelf-080725-1016-16-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/built-in-bookshelf-080725-1016-16-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/built-in-bookshelf-080725-1016-16-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/built-in-bookshelf-080725-1016-16-1536x2048.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe bathroom embraces texture with a mix of tile and book-matched Calacatta verde marble. Five slabs form a seamless wall of subtle geometry. A band of glass blocks brings in natural light, offering a nostalgic nod to 1980s design while remaining highly functional.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2288\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/contemporary-pastel-green-bathroom-080725-1016-17.jpg\" alt=\"Calacatta verde marble, soft tile, and retro glass blocks bring luxury and light into this modern Montreal bathroom with timeless flair.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/contemporary-pastel-green-bathroom-080725-1016-17.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/contemporary-pastel-green-bathroom-080725-1016-17-940x1120.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/contemporary-pastel-green-bathroom-080725-1016-17-800x953.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/contemporary-pastel-green-bathroom-080725-1016-17-768x915.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/contemporary-pastel-green-bathroom-080725-1016-17-1289x1536.jpg 1289w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/contemporary-pastel-green-bathroom-080725-1016-17-1719x2048.jpg 1719w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1281\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/contemporary-pastel-green-bathroom-080725-1016-18.jpg\" alt=\"Calacatta verde marble, soft tile, and retro glass blocks bring luxury and light into this modern Montreal bathroom with timeless flair.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/contemporary-pastel-green-bathroom-080725-1016-18.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/contemporary-pastel-green-bathroom-080725-1016-18-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/contemporary-pastel-green-bathroom-080725-1016-18-800x534.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/contemporary-pastel-green-bathroom-080725-1016-18-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/contemporary-pastel-green-bathroom-080725-1016-18-1536x1025.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/contemporary-pastel-green-bathroom-080725-1016-19.jpg\" alt=\"Calacatta verde marble, soft tile, and retro glass blocks bring luxury and light into this modern Montreal bathroom with timeless flair.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/contemporary-pastel-green-bathroom-080725-1016-19.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/contemporary-pastel-green-bathroom-080725-1016-19-940x1253.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/contemporary-pastel-green-bathroom-080725-1016-19-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/contemporary-pastel-green-bathroom-080725-1016-19-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/contemporary-pastel-green-bathroom-080725-1016-19-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/contemporary-pastel-green-bathroom-080725-1016-19-1536x2048.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eIn the master suite, custom cabinets do more than store clothes. One cleverly hides the owners’ wine collection, revealing how every element in Elmire blends purpose with personal meaning.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1703\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/bedroom-with-wood-closets-080725-1016-20.jpg\" alt=\"In this serene loft bedroom, custom cabinetry hides both essentials and surprises—including a wine collection. Modern comfort with a personal twist.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/bedroom-with-wood-closets-080725-1016-20.jpg 1703w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/bedroom-with-wood-closets-080725-1016-20-940x1413.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/bedroom-with-wood-closets-080725-1016-20-800x1203.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/bedroom-with-wood-closets-080725-1016-20-768x1154.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/bedroom-with-wood-closets-080725-1016-20-1022x1536.jpg 1022w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/bedroom-with-wood-closets-080725-1016-20-1362x2048.jpg 1362w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1703px) 100vw, 1703px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eLa Firme’s thoughtful intervention doesn’t overwrite the building’s past but enriches it, proving that true transformation begins with listening, to the structure, the context, and the people who will call it home.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003ePhotographer: \u003ca href=\"https://www.yulphoto.ca/\"\u003eUlysse Lemerise\u003c/a\u003e | Architects/designers: La Firme | Cabinet work: Atelier 13 | Natural stone: Ateliers Stoneage | Lighting: Lambert et Fils\u003c/h6\u003e\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
